{
  "stem": "10098.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they started to question me, and-- like asking me questions if anybody in my family had been sick, or mentally retarded, or any disease.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I told him no, nobody in my family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then I went back, he give me that candy and that sandwich.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the trucks were waiting, and they took us back to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I start-- I told my friends what happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They told me, you better stay away from there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Don't go over there, because they gonna suck you dry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was a little weak when I can recall, I was so scared in-- in the wilderness-- I don't know what kind of [? words. ?] I see something different happen, which I thought-- when I got back he really scared me, one of the fellas.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He said, you could fill out, you know, when too much blood you give.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then again, I went working in-- to Buchenwald, to Weimar.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The bombs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even I went into the kitchen and found a lot of onions, and I put it in my pants, the onions.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we came in to Buchenwald, in the prison, we have to jump.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "About four or five people hold hands.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "While I was jumping all the onions fell out, and the SS took me out and beat the crap out of me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They beat me up bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And was waiting-- for the night shift was waiting another group, PWs-- POWs, Russians, to go in to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Nazi SS told the Russian to get the onions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So when I left, after he beat me up, the Russians call me back-- [SPEAKING RUSSIAN] in Russian-- and they give me all the onions back, the Russians.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were prisoners, too, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were going to work, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
